com.espertech.esper.epl.expression.time

Class ExprTimePeriodImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.espertech.esper.epl.expression.core.ExprNodeBase
      • com.espertech.esper.epl.expression.time.ExprTimePeriodImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExprNode, ExprNodeRenderable, ExprValidator, ExprTimePeriod, java.io.Serializable

    public class ExprTimePeriodImpl
extends ExprNodeBase
implements ExprTimePeriod
    Expression representing a time period.

    Child nodes to this expression carry the actual parts and must return a numeric value.
